# Invisible empty tile - degenerate quad at Y=0
# Extents: X/Z -0.5..0.5, Y=0 (zero height, fully degenerate area)
# Renders nothing, but provides valid bounds for editor / collider / culling systems.

o empty_tile

# Four vertices forming a 1x1 square on the XZ plane at Y=0
v -0.5  0.0 -0.5
v  0.5  0.0 -0.5
v  0.5  0.0  0.5
v -0.5  0.0  0.5

# One normal (direction doesn't matter much since area=0)
vn 0 1 0

# Four degenerate triangles around the perimeter (all have zero area)
# This forces the bounding box to be correct while rendering nothing.
f 1//1 2//1 2//1
f 2//1 3//1 3//1
f 3//1 4//1 4//1
f 4//1 1//1 1//1